alpha.

DBF - Database Backend Frontend

Database Model {
    ORM interface,
    migrations,
    schema
}

Backend for Model {
    Router
    Logic (remote modules)
}

Frontend for Model [
    admin:{
        Route
        Component / Mixin/RemoteModule(Frontend Logic)
        views:[
            index
            show
            create
            edit
        ]
    },
    public:{
        Route
        Component / Mixin/RemoteModule(Frontend Logic)
    }
]
an admin page has a public frontend counterpart with an admin prefixed route

all these are by reference
project:{
    models:{
        appsterjsmodule: 'main'
        app:{
            components:{
                frontend:{
                    admin:{
                        middleware
                        route
                        components: {
                            index
                            show
                            create
                            edit
                        }
                    }
                    public:{
                        middleware
                        content
                        route
                    }
                }
                backend:{
                    appsterjsmodule
                }
            }
        }
        users:{
            roles -> for middleware
        }
    }
    migrations
}

create structure for model, view and controller to be managed by a remote module.
create a module that displays the database and migrations. (implement basic migrate/undo/etc commands)
create a module that displays the routes. (implement route modules)
create a module that edits components.
create a module that creates mvc models.
create a module that manages a project. (project->modules->pages->etc)

beta.

associate modules to users.
implement password encryption and login logic.
implement register logic.
create a module that displays server files and allows edits.
implement a better logging system.
list the console output into the browser. (move after completion to later, implement IO for this console)
transparent error checking all the way.

Gold.